JOHANNESBURG - Ennerdale residents are demanding a meeting with Johannesburg Mayor Herman Mashaba.They say it s the only thing that will get them off the streets.READ: Ennerdale community tired of being overlookedProtesting residents blocked roads and engaged in running battles with police on Tuesday, calling for RDP housing allocations.They have accused authorities of failing to deliver on their problems.Community members say they feel they have been ignored by the ANC government.eNCA